Welcome to the code for the iAppsForStudents website. This site hosts an annual sale for Mac, iPhone and iPad applications specifically for students.


Gems:
aws-s3


Plugins:

script/plugin install git://github.com/adamwiggins/gmail_smtp.git
script/plugin install git://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip.git
   *note that paperclip requires ImageMagick to run: www.imagemagick.org


Environment:

GMAIL_SMTP_USER
GMAIL_SMTP_PASSWORD
S3_ACCESSKEY
S3_SECRETKEY
S3_BUCKET
